<BaseLayout title="About · AI Tools Reviews & Tutorials" description="About this site: a personal blog focused on AI tool reviews and tutorials, helping you find tools that actually work." lang="en">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>About</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="prose">
    <p>Hi, I'm nyy — a regular internet user who spends a lot of time with AI tools.</p>

    <p>I've made plenty of mistakes along the way: paid for tools that weren't worth it, hit paywalls on free tiers, struggled with confusing tutorials. Over time I developed my own way of evaluating tools, and decided to write it all down so others don't have to repeat the same trial and error.</p>

    <p>This blog focuses exclusively on AI tools — reviews, how-to guides, and buying advice. It covers AI chat, writing, image generation, coding assistants, and video tools, with a particular focus on options that are accessible, free, or offer strong value for money.</p>

    <p>The review standard is simple: sign up and use it myself, give a concrete verdict, and note when the test was done. AI tools move fast — outdated articles get updated as things change.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
